text: Greta Georgieva (; born 19 April 1965) is a Bulgarian rowing coxswain. She competed in two events at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Bulgaria Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Coxswains (rowing)
